{"id":"errors/NG0504","title":"NG0504: ngSkipHydration 屬性被新增到不是元件宿主的元素上。","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng0504-the-ngskiphydration-attribute-was-added-to-an-element-that-is-not-a-component-host\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1wube4gm4jki2kw9em57ajh02\">NG0504: ngSkipHydration 屬性被新增到不是元件宿主的元素上。<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG0504#ng0504-the-ngskiphydration-attribute-was-added-to-an-element-that-is-not-a-component-host\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  \n  \n\n  <div class=\"error-description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG0504#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"32d1f4zwwhct8q958f9dsxkk\">當 <code>ngSkipHydration</code> 屬性被新增到不合適的 DOM 節點時，就會發生此錯誤。<code>ngSkipHydration</code> 屬性只能直接在樣板中或透過宿主繫結應用於元件的宿主節點。它不能應用於其他 DOM 節點，如果這樣做除了導致本錯誤之外不會有任何效果。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7y3d3wqt0871xkjy4t3o0x73k\">有關水合的更多訊息，請參閱<a href=\"guide/hydration\">本指南</a>。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"arzd8spphyexzbiuw3akgoz23\">以下範例將引發錯誤。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d8z36ytglnshcm1ca5odpqisa\"><strong>範例 1：</strong></p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2w2ls6vt1dc4poo4t7jhik42a\">在此範例中，<code>ngSkipHydration</code> 屬性被應用於使用指令進行宿主繫結的 <code>&lt;div&gt;</code>。由於 <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> 不是元件宿主節點，所以 Angular 會丟擲錯誤。</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({\n  standalone: true,\n  selector: '[dir]',\n  host: {ngSkipHydration: 'true'},\n})\nclass Dir {\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  standalone: true,\n  selector: 'app',\n  imports: [Dir],\n  template: `\n    &lt;div dir&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n  `,\n})\nclass SimpleComponent {\n}\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7xvrml7ymv0le8a1c4xvd1sm7\"><strong>範例 2：</strong></p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2iks644srfgzz83evlcgubs3y\">在此範例中，<code>ngSkipHydration</code> 透過樣板作為屬性應用於 <code>&lt;div&gt;</code>。由於 <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> 不是元件的宿主節點，所以 Angular 會丟擲錯誤。</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  standalone: true,\n  selector: 'app',\n  template: `\n    &lt;div ngSkipHydration&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n  `,\n})\nclass SimpleComponent {\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  </div>\n\n\n  \n  <br>\n\n  <div class=\"debugging\">\n    <h2 id=\"debugging-the-error\">如何排除本錯誤<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG0504#debugging-the-error\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9t81w5a8opsovfyrbze2ouetm\">從所有無效的 DOM 節點中刪除 <code>ngSkipHydration</code> 屬性。或者，在樣板中或透過宿主繫結將 <code>ngSkipHydration</code> 屬性移動到元件宿主節點。</p>\n\n  </div>\n  \n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - errors\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Directive\n - errors/NG0504#debugging-the-error\n - errors/NG0504#description\n - errors/NG0504#ng0504-the-ngskiphydration-attribute-was-added-to-an-element-that-is-not-a-component-host\n - guide/hydration\n-->"}